<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Marcia_Angell" title="Marcia Angell">Angell, Marcia</a> (2009), "Drug Companies &amp; Doctors: A Story of Corruption", <i><a href="/wiki/New_York_Review_of_Books" title="New York Review of Books" class="mw-redirect">New York Review of Books</a></i>, Vol 56, No 1; 15 January 2009.</li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24" title="">^</a></b> Angell M. (2004). The Truth About Drug Companies, p. 30.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Say_no-25"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Say_no_25-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSox_HC.2C_Rennie_D2008">Sox HC, Rennie D (August 2008). "<a href="http://www.annals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=18711161" class="external text" title="http://www.annals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=18711161" rel="nofollow">Seeding trials: just say "no"</a>". <i>Ann. Intern. Med.</i> <b>149</b> (4): 279–80. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18711161" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18711161">PMID 18711161</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.annals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=18711161" class="external free" title="http://www.annals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=18711161" rel="nofollow">http://www.annals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=18711161</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-08-21</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Seeding+trials%3A+just+say+%22no%22&amp;rft.jtitle=Ann.+Intern.+Med.&amp;rft.aulast=Sox+HC%2C+Rennie+D&amp;rft.au=Sox+HC%2C+Rennie+D&amp;rft.date=August+2008&amp;rft.volume=149&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=279%E2%80%9380&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/18711161&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.annals.org%2Fcgi%2Fpmidlookup%3Fview%3Dlong%26pmid%3D18711161&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Clinical_trial"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
